abstract: New York Jets linebacker Aaron Maybin, who was cut twice in the preseason before the Jets re-signed him, has forced three fumbles in the last games.
snippet: Since being signed by the Jets for a second time late last month, Aaron Maybin has forced three fumbles in the last games.
lead_paragraph: Since being signed by the Jets for a second time late last month, Aaron Maybin has forced three fumbles in the last games.

headline.main: Given a Second Chance, a Jets Linebacker Wraps It Up
